Charles Quatermaine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Quatermaine 0 Charles Quatermaine (30 December 1877 in Richmond, Surrey – August 1958 in Sussex) was a British stage and film actor. He also appeared on Broadway. He was the second husband of actress Mary Forbes, and brother of Leon Quartermaine.
